-- Standard Chartered Names Haigh Commodity Research Head Based in Singapore
-- Yee Kai Pin
-- 2010-07-26T09:15:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-26/standard-chartered-names-haigh-commodity-research-head-based-in-singapore.html

          
          
             Standard Chartered Plc named Michael
Haigh as global head of commodities research based in Singapore,
the company said in a statement today.  
